Individual




Shelley G. Broader



Ms. Shelley G. Broader is President, Chief Executive Officer & Director at Chico's FAS, Inc. and Independent Non-Executive Director at Raymond James Financial, Inc. She is on the Board of Directors at Chico's FAS, Inc. and Raymond James Financial, Inc.
Ms. Broader was previously employed as Non-Executive Director by Massmart Holdings Ltd., President, Chief Executive Officer & EVP by Walmart EMEA Ltd., President & Chief Executive Officer by Wal-Mart Canada Corp., Senior Vice President by Sam's West, Inc., President & Chief Operating Officer by Michaels Stores, Inc., President & Chief Executive Officer by Kash N' Karry Food Stores LLC, SVP-Business Strategy, Marketing & Communications by Hannaford Bros. Co. LLC, an Assistant Vice President by First Albany Corp., and a Trustee by Saint Leo University, Inc. She also served on the board at Wal-Mart de México SAB de CV and United Way of Tampa Bay.
She received her undergraduate degree from Washington State University.



